1
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,400
Maybe it was God's blessing,

2
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:13,300
that Xiao Lu, whom I had been longing for,

3
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,840
suddenly appeared before my eyes.

4
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:15,400
Please.

5
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:16,880
Let me go.

6
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:20,360
But I had never seen her like that.

7
00:02:20,760 --> 00:02:21,600
Let me go.

8
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,860
She was skin and bones,

9
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:28,079
like wild grass that could snap in the wind at any moment.

10
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,400
She didn't recognize me.

11
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:36,340
But I recognized her at first glance.

12
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,240
Please,

13
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:46,320
let me go.

14
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,720
I don't want to miss

15
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:52,520
this only chance to connect with her.

16
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,720
So I spoke up.

17
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:55,960
Wait.

18
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,400
Do you think

19
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,800
you can get out like this?

20
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:15,560
Clean up.

21
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:18,090
I'll take you with me later.

22
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,560
I know she killed Li Ting.

23
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:46,560
But

24
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:48,930
I wanted to save her.

25
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:01,240
Isn't this Zhao?

26
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,200
Zhao,

27
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,080
are you still mad?

28
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:08,880
Lu.

29
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,160
That was fast.

30
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,800
I avoided the surveillance cameras along the way.

31
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:33,159
Lu told me what happened to her.

32
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,280
At that moment,

33
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:38,280
I realized that

34
00:04:38,280 --> 00:04:39,280
in this world,

35
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,000
except for me,

36
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,159
no one could help her.

37
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:07,320
I figured you would soon discover the dumbwaiter.

38
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:10,760
Only by gaining weight in a short time

39
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:13,520
could Lu dispel your suspicions.

40
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,850
The confession is basically true.

41
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,240
Okay.

42
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:23,920
Officer,

43
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:26,720
you must not tell Lu

44
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:29,730
that I was the one who led Li Ting to her.

45
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,640
Even without you,

46
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,900
there would be others.

47
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,400
But because of you,

48
00:05:36,080 --> 00:05:38,040
she at least had some hope,

49
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:38,880
didn't she?

50
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:41,760
Officer,

51
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:44,640
can I see her one more time?

52
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,520
I'm sorry

53
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,250
for dragging you into this.

54
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,080
It's all over.

55
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:09,320
Let's go.

56
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,280
Let's go.

57
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,480
Lu,

58
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:14,040
don't give up.

59
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:15,720
I will wait for you.

60
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:26,360
You spent half a month

61
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,760
gaining 20 pounds.

62
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:29,220
It must have been painful.

63
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:34,000
Compared to the torture over the years,

64
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,080
it's nothing.

65
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,090
I thought getting rid of Li Ting

66
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,440
and being with Dong would be my new life.

67
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,159
But someone like me

68
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:47,210
probably doesn't deserve happiness.

69
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:48,960
Someone like you?

70
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,890
What kind of person are you?

71
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:53,320
If you choose to abandon yourself,

72
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,340
what about those who love you?

73
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:57,120
Lu Chen.

74
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,400
Although you killed someone,

75
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:01,960
the judge will consider your long-term domestic violence

76
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:03,840
and personal safety issues.

77
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:06,400
They will definitely lighten your sentence.

78
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,530
You are still young.

79
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,730
Rehabilitate well inside.

80
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:12,600
I believe you will soon regain your freedom.

81
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:14,240
And Dong Shan said

82
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,960
he is willing to wait for you.

83
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:17,600
You must cherish

84
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,600
your life.

85
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,160
Officer Zhuang,

86
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:24,320
Mr. Cheng,

87
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:25,880
thank you.

88
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:31,320
Lu Chen,

89
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:35,040
you said Li Ting forced you into that room.

90
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,560
Then you couldn't possibly know

91
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,159
there was a dumbwaiter in it.

92
00:07:38,840 --> 00:07:41,440
Someone must have taught you how to clean up the traces

93
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:42,680
and escape the scene.

94
00:07:43,159 --> 00:07:45,720
Can you tell me who that person was?

95
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,440
I don't know who he is.

96
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,360
I only remember that day,

97
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:51,880
after Li Ting died,

98
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:53,760
I was very scared.

99
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:57,440
Suddenly, the phone in the room rang.

100
00:07:58,200 --> 00:08:01,840
The ringing was like a death warrant,

101
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:05,480
reminding me that this couldn't be kept a secret.

102
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:08,320
So I decided to answer the phone

103
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,760
and face it calmly.

104
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,560
Hello.

105
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,720
Room service.

106
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:19,360
It seems Mr. Li is not available.

107
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:21,160
So the person answering the phone now

108
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:23,040
must be Ms. Lu Chen.

109
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,640
How do you know?

110
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:27,520
Since you are able to answer the phone now,

111
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:29,280
can I assume

112
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:31,320
that Mr. Li Ting had an accident,

113
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:33,760
or is he already...

114
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:37,380
It seems it went smoother than expected.

115
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:38,480
If so,

116
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:40,559
I can give you a chance, Ms. Lu.

117
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,080
What chance?

118
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:44,960
A chance for you to regain your freedom.

119
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,640
I don't need it.

120
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:48,240
Lu Chen.

121
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:50,680
I know you want to turn yourself in now,

122
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:52,810
but as soon as you walk out of that door,

123
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:55,200
your life will be ruined.

124
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:58,160
I have a way to get you off the hook.

125
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:58,960
Trust me.

126
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:00,120
Do as I say.

127
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,000
First,

128
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,720
get rid of all your traces in the room,

129
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:08,320
including fingerprints, hair, and blood.

130
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:11,640
Then turn the AC down to the lowest setting.

131
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:13,640
Second,

132
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,560
behind the solid wood cabinet in the entryway,

133
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:17,520
there is an abandoned dumbwaiter.

134
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,760
With your current weight,

135
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:21,890
you should be able to leave through it.

136
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,840
You asked her why she helped you.

137
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,080
What did she say?

138
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:29,460
I only remember her saying one thing:

139
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,680
Life is dark,

140
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:34,360
but the Lighthouse shines forever.

141
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,400
Your hunch was right.

142
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:41,120
Lighthouse has struck again.

143
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:44,640
How did they know Lu Chen wanted to kill Li Ting?

144
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:47,720
It must be a premeditated setup,

145
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,520
turning all chances

146
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,680
into inevitabilities.

147
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:56,000
Their people must be hiding in the dark,

148
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,720
watching our every move,

149
00:09:58,400 --> 00:10:01,600
to ensure the whole case becomes a dead end.

150
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,880
When Lu Chen left the room,

151
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:08,280
the dumbwaiter was exposed.

152
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:14,160
Then someone must have restored the cabinet from the outside.

153
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,080
Liu Ying.

154
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,980
She's the discoverer.

155
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:22,080
Before we arrived at the scene,

156
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,840
she was the only one who entered the room.

157
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:27,440
She was the only one with the opportunity to restore the cabinet.

158
00:10:29,520 --> 00:10:30,560
It must be her.

159
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,680
Because she's a cleaner,

160
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:34,720
it was too easy for her to do all this.

161
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,560
She also provided the time Lu Chen left the hotel.

162
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:38,560
It really is her.

163
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:41,010
She is the designer of Lighthouse.

164
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:52,600
I didn't expect the truth to be like this.

165
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,770
Who would have thought?

166
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:57,560
To think of such a way to clear suspicion.

167
00:10:58,320 --> 00:11:00,120
Do you think her body can take it?

168
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,200
Amazing.

169
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,890
Captain Zhuang is calling.

170
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:10,360
Hello, Captain Zhuang.

171
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:12,800
Find out where Liu Ying lives right away.

172
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,400
She's a major suspect.

173
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:15,560
Send me the location.

174
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:17,600
Bring your weapons and meet at Liu Ying's place.

175
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,320
Oh, okay.

176
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,380
I'll go find it now.

177
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:20,600
Xiaobai.

178
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:26,200
Slow down.

179
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:26,600
Captain Zhuang.

180
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:28,660
Liu Ying's room is on the third floor.

181
00:11:28,920 --> 00:11:29,920
I really didn't expect

182
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:31,000
it to be her.

183
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:42,690
Captain Zhuang.

184
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:45,240
It seems she's been gone for a while.

185
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:01,890
Hello, Old Shao.

186
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:02,970
Captain Zhuang.

187
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:04,840
After Lu Chen confessed,

188
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:06,000
I immediately took her fingerprints

189
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,840
and the prints left on that half ring,

190
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:08,960
including Liu Ying's,

191
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,280
and compared them repeatedly.

192
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:11,560
The final results show

193
00:12:11,880 --> 00:12:13,610
they belong to neither of them.

194
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,920
The fingerprints are neither Lu Chen's

195
00:12:17,920 --> 00:12:19,120
nor Liu Ying's,

196
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:19,800
right?

197
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:27,440
This half fingerprint happened to be left in the dumbwaiter.

198
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,840
I just don't understand

199
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:33,280
why he would do this.
